<h1><i class="fa fa-gift"></i>Benefits</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><i class="fa fa-gift"></i>Benefits</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p>Running your own personal <%= application.name %> for your company, department, or lab, has a number of key benefits. </p>

	<div class="attention"><div class="emphasis">How <%= application.name %> Can Benefit You</div></div>

	<div class="details section" style="margin-top:30px">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Features</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Self-hostable </li>
					<li>Privacy and security </li>
					<li>Easy and intuitive user interface </li>
					<li>Integrated sharing features </li>
					<li>Customizable </li>
					<li>Brandable </li>
					<li>Free as in speech (open) </li>
					<li>Free as in beer (gratis) </li>
					<li>Non-proprietery </li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-star"></i>Benefits</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Take back control. </li>
					<li>Keep your data private. </li>
					<li>Enjoy a superior user experience. </li>
					<li>Collaborate with friends and colleagues. </li>
					<li>Configure the platform to suit your needs. </li>
					<li>Express your brand. </li>
					<li>Feel secure about your platform. </li>
					<li>Save money for yourself or your organization. </li>
					<li>Support independence and diversity. </li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-hand-fist"></i>Take Back Control</h2>
				<p><%= application.name %> allows you to take back control over your data.  You can free yourself from the whims of large corporations.  You no longer have to worry about changing business models, changing policies, or becoming caught in the crossfire of corporate takeovers. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img src="images/info/benefits/fist.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-lock"></i>Keep Your Data Private</h2>
				<p>By running your own platform, you can free yourself from surveillance, overzealous content moderation, and targeted advertising. You can determine your own policies and you can escape from being digitally profiled. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img src="images/info/benefits/safe.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-smile"></i>Enjoy Your Cloud</h2>
				<p><%= application.name %> has been designed to be easy and intuitive to use.  It has been modeled after systems that your users are already familiar with so they can spend their time using the platform instead of figuring out how to use it. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img src="images/info/benefits/smile.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-share"></i>Collaborate and Share</h2>
				<p><%= application.name %> lets you set up a private and secure environment for sharing files and messages with friends and colleagues. Share sensitive or proprietary information. <%= application.name %> can become your shared private collaborative space.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img src="images/info/benefits/comments.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-gears"></i>Customize Your Platform</h2>
				<p><%= application.name %> has a wide range of options for easy configuration and customization.  Instead of using the platform handed down by the tech giants, you can make the platform your own. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img src="images/info/benefits/gear.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-paint-brush"></i>Express Your Brand</h2>
				<p>Your <%= application.name %> can be branded to match the brand identity of your company or organization.  You can configure the platform to use the logos, colors, fonts, and verbiage that you want. By branding the platform, you can use the platform to promote and express your brand. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img src="images/info/benefits/paint-brush.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-life-ring"></i>Feel More Secure</h2>
				<p>Since the code of <%= application.name %> is open, you know how and where your data is stored and what is happening when you store or share data.  <%= application.name %> in not a black box like commercial / proprietary platforms where you have to take their word for what is happening with your data. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img src="images/info/benefits/no-questions.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-money-bill"></i>Save Money</h2>
				<p><%= application.name %> is free of charge. Aside from the cost of hosting, running your platform is free.  This can save you money over commercial / proprietary solutions.  Since you control the platform, you don't need to be worried about surprise pricing changes from a commercial platform. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img src="images/info/benefits/money.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-flag-usa"></i>Support Independence</h2>
				<p>By running your own platform, you are making a statement that independence and diversity in the tech ecosystem are important to you. You can opt out of supporting the large, predatory and monopolistic corporations that dominate today's tech landscape. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img src="images/info/benefits/liberty.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>